                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-748-18770917 t18770917-748-punishment-62"></join>Twelve Months' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
